~250 make poison<br>
~200 apply poison<br>
~250 brewing :P<br>
<br>
I personally would just like poisons to be unresistable.  Come to think of it..that would be a nice addition to Poison Mastery 3 (seeing as no one wants it in the current state:x)<br>
<br>
I'm sorry but spending 3 hours in the Emerald Jungle on my barely able to solo the mobs ranger who is actually able to track the blasted things for 10 chances at making a poison (only to fail 7), is not worth the trouble when the 3 you actually do succeed in making are resisted by anything you try them on.<br>
<br>
